com.devisubox.dvws.Runnable

Class SendingThread

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.devisubox.dvws.Runnable.SendingThread
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class SendingThread
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable
    The Class SendingThread, that executes all the instructions given by the dvws client. For building a SendingThread, see the SendingThread.SendingThreadBuilder class.
